content: Provided a bulleted list of all the different Star Trek television series, in order of oldest to newest. Include the name of the main starships or stations from each series and the captain of these starships.

chosen:
Here is a bulleted list of all the Star Trek television series, listed in order from oldest to newest:
- Star Trek: The Original Series (1966–1969) - USS Enterprise, Captain James T. Kirk
- Star Trek: The Animated Series (1973–1974) - USS Enterprise, Captain James T. Kirk
- Star Trek: Phase II (1978–1979) - USS Enterprise, Captain Jean-Luc Picard
- Star Trek: The Next Generation (1987–1994) - USS Enterprise-D, Captain Jean-Luc Picard
- Star Trek: Deep Space Nine (1993–1999) - USS Defiant, Captain Sisko
- Star Trek: Voyager (1995–2001) - USS Voyager, Captain Kathryn Janeway
- Star Trek: Enterprise (2001–2005) - USS Enterprise (NX-01), Captain Archer
- Star Trek: Discovery (2017–present) - USS Discovery, Captain Gabriel Lorca
- Star Trek: Picard (2020–present) - La Sirena, Captain Jean-Luc Picard
- Star Trek: Lower Decks (2020–present) - USS Cerritos, Captain Freeman
